4,4,5,5-tetramethyl-2-(4,4,5,5-tetramethyl-1,3,2-dioxaborolan-2-yl)-1,3,2-dioxaborolane and (6s)-3-[(1s)-1-(4-bromophenyl)ethyl]-6-(4-fluorophenyl)-6-(2-hydroxy-2-methylpropyl)-1,3-oxazinan-2-one react together in the presence of acetate, ethyl acetate, methylsulfinylmethane, potassium(1+) to produce (6s)-6-(4-fluorophenyl)-6-(2-hydroxy-2-methylpropyl)-3-[(1s)-1-[4-(4,4,5,5-tetramethyl-1,3,2-dioxaborolan-2-yl)phenyl]ethyl]-1,3-oxazinan-2-one.

N-methylmethanamine and 7-methoxy-3,4-dihydro-2h-naphthalen-1-one react together in the presence of toluene, tetrachlorotitanium, titanium to produce 7-methoxy-n,n-dimethyl-3,4-dihydronaphthalen-1-amine.

2-[4-[3-(6-fluoropyridin-2-yl)-1-(oxan-2-yl)pyrazolo[3,4-c]pyridin-5-yl]pyrazol-1-yl]acetic acid and azanium react together in the presence of chloride to produce 2-[4-[3-(6-fluoropyridin-2-yl)-1-(oxan-2-yl)pyrazolo[3,4-c]pyridin-5-yl]pyrazol-1-yl]acetamide.

Acetyl acetate and 4-[4-bromo-2-(trifluoromethyl)phenyl]sulfonylmorpholine react together in the presence of oxolane, magnesium;propane;chloride, ethyl acetate, oxidane, hydrogen carbonate, sodium(1+) to produce 1-[4-morpholin-4-ylsulfonyl-3-(trifluoromethyl)phenyl]ethanone.
Methyl 4-bromo-2-(2,4-difluorophenoxy)butanoate reacts in the presence of oxolane, 2-methylpropan-2-olate, potassium(1+) to produce methyl 1-(2,4-difluorophenoxy)cyclopropane-1-carboxylate.
2-[benzyl(methyl)amino]-n-(2-nitrophenyl)acetamide reacts in the presence of methanol, oxoplatinum, molecular hydrogen to produce n-(2-aminophenyl)-2-[benzyl(methyl)amino]acetamide.

2-ethoxy-5-(4,4,5,5-tetramethyl-1,3,2-dioxaborolan-2-yl)-3-(trifluoromethyl)pyridine and 6-(4-bromofuran-2-yl)-1-[(2,4-difluorophenyl)methyl]-2-oxo-4-(trifluoromethyl)pyridine-3-carbonitrile react together in the presence of [6-ethoxy-5-(trifluoromethyl)pyridin-3-yl]boronic acid, 1,2-dimethoxyethane, oxidane, carbonate, potassium(1+), palladium;triphenylphosphanium to produce 1-[(2,4-difluorophenyl)methyl]-6-[4-[6-ethoxy-5-(trifluoromethyl)pyridin-3-yl]furan-2-yl]-2-oxo-4-(trifluoromethyl)pyridine-3-carbonitrile.
Bromomethylbenzene and 4-bromo-2-(hydroxymethyl)phenol react together in the presence of ethanol, sodium(1+), hydroxide to produce (5-bromo-2-phenylmethoxyphenyl)methanol.
Tert-butyl n-[(4-bromo-3-methylbenzoyl)amino]carbamate reacts in the presence of acetic acid, dichloromethane to produce 4-bromo-3-methylbenzohydrazide.

(1s)-1-phenylethanamine and 2-(trifluoromethyl)cyclohexan-1-one react together in the presence of triacetyloxyboranuide, 1,2-dichloroethane, hydrogen carbonate, sodium(1+) to produce (1r,2s)-n-[(1r)-1-phenylethyl]-2-(trifluoromethyl)cyclohexan-1-amine.
But-3-en-2-one and 6-nitro-1,3-benzodioxol-5-amine react together to produce 9-methyl-5-nitro-[1,3]dioxolo[4,5-f]quinoline.

4-[5-(hydroxymethyl)tetrazol-1-yl]-2-(trifluoromethyl)benzonitrile and thionyl dichloride react together in the presence of toluene to produce 4-[5-(chloromethyl)tetrazol-1-yl]-2-(trifluoromethyl)benzonitrile.
Oxolane and 4-chloro-2-hydroxybenzaldehyde react together in the presence of carbonate, cesium(1+) to produce 4-chloro-2-prop-2-enoxybenzaldehyde.

Phosphoryl trichloride and 3-nitro-5-(trifluoromethyl)-1h-pyridin-2-one react together in the presence of acetonitrile, benzyl(trimethyl)azanium, oxidane, chloride to produce 2-chloro-3-nitro-5-(trifluoromethyl)pyridine.

(5-methylsulfanylpyridin-3-yl)-(2-tributylstannylimidazo[5,1-b][1,3]thiazol-7-yl)methanone and (4-nitrophenyl)methyl (2r,4r,5r,6s)-6-[(1r)-1-hydroxyethyl]-4-methyl-3,7-dioxo-1-azabicyclo[3.2.0]heptane-2-carboxylate react together to produce (4-nitrophenyl)methyl (4s,5r,6s)-6-[(1r)-1-hydroxyethyl]-4-methyl-3-[7-(5-methylsulfanylpyridine-3-carbonyl)imidazo[5,1-b][1,3]thiazol-2-yl]-7-oxo-1-azabicyclo[3.2.0]hept-2-ene-2-carboxylate.

Methyl n-[5-(bromomethyl)-1,2-oxazol-3-yl]carbamate and 6-cyclopentyl-6-[2-(4-methoxyphenyl)ethyl]oxane-2,4-dione react together in the presence of 5-(chloromethyl)-1,3-dimethyl-1,2,4-triazole to produce methyl n-[5-[[2-cyclopentyl-4-hydroxy-2-[2-(4-methoxyphenyl)ethyl]-6-oxo-3h-pyran-5-yl]methyl]-1,2-oxazol-3-yl]carbamate.

1-(1,1-dioxo-3,5-dihydro-2h-1lambda6,4-benzothiazepin-4-yl)ethanone and 2-amino-5-methylbenzonitrile react together in the presence of dichloromethane, oxidane, hydrogen carbonate, phosphoryl trichloride, sodium(1+) to produce 2-[1-(1,1-dioxo-3,5-dihydro-2h-1lambda6,4-benzothiazepin-4-yl)ethylideneamino]-5-methylbenzonitrile.

Morpholine and tert-butyl (2s)-2-(hydroxymethyl)pyrrolidine-1-carboxylate react together in the presence of n,n-diethylethanamine, methanesulfonyl chloride, toluene, dichloromethane to produce tert-butyl (2s)-2-(morpholin-4-ylmethyl)pyrrolidine-1-carboxylate.

N-ethyl-n-propan-2-ylpropan-2-amine and 4,6-dichloro-2-methylsulfanylpyrimidine react together in the presence of oxolane, n-methylmethanamine, oxidane to produce 6-chloro-n,n-dimethyl-2-methylsulfanylpyrimidin-4-amine.

1-(5-tert-butyl-1,2-oxazol-3-yl)-3-(3-hydroxyphenyl)urea and 4-chloro-7-methoxy-5-(oxan-4-yloxy)quinazoline react together in the presence of propan-2-ol, carbonate, cesium(1+) to produce 1-(5-tert-butyl-1,2-oxazol-3-yl)-3-[3-[7-methoxy-5-(oxan-4-yloxy)quinazolin-4-yl]oxyphenyl]urea.

2-methylbutan-2-amine and phenyl n'-[3,5-bis(trifluoromethyl)phenyl]-n-cyanocarbamimidate react together in the presence of acetonitrile, n,n-diethylethanamine to produce 1-[3,5-bis(trifluoromethyl)phenyl]-3-cyano-2-(2-methylbutan-2-yl)guanidine.
(2-methylnaphthalen-1-yl)boronic acid and 1-bromo-2-methylnaphthalene react together in the presence of boronic acid, hydrogen peroxide to produce 2-methylnaphthalen-1-ol.
Ethyl 3,7-dimethyl-1h-indole-2-carboxylate reacts in the presence of oxolane, aluminum(3+), hydride, lithium(1+) to produce (3,7-dimethyl-1h-indol-2-yl)methanol.
Methyl 1h-indole-5-carboxylate reacts in the presence of acetic acid, oxidane, cyanoboranuide, sodium(1+), hydroxide to produce methyl 2,3-dihydro-1h-indole-5-carboxylate.

[(2s,4r)-4-[(4-methoxyphenyl)methylsulfanyl]-1-methylsulfonylpyrrolidin-2-yl]methyl methanesulfonate and phenylmethanamine react together in the presence of iodide, sodium(1+) to produce n-benzyl-1-[(2s,4r)-4-[(4-methoxyphenyl)methylsulfanyl]-1-methylsulfonylpyrrolidin-2-yl]methanamine.

Ethyl 3-aminopropanoate and 4-[[cyclohexyl-(3-methylthieno[3,2-b]pyridin-2-yl)methyl]amino]benzoic acid react together in the presence of n,n-diethylethanamine, 3-(ethyliminomethylideneamino)-n,n-dimethylpropan-1-amine, n,n-dimethylformamide, chlorane, oxidane, 1-hydroxybenzotriazole, chloride, azanium to produce ethyl 3-[[4-[[cyclohexyl-(3-methylthieno[3,2-b]pyridin-2-yl)methyl]amino]benzoyl]amino]propanoate.

2-[4-[(4-chlorophenyl)-phenylmethyl]piperazin-1-yl]ethanamine and 5-(4-cyclohexylphenyl)-1-phenylpyrazole-3-carbaldehyde react together to produce 2-[4-[(4-chlorophenyl)-phenylmethyl]piperazin-1-yl]-n-[[5-(4-cyclohexylphenyl)-1-phenylpyrazol-3-yl]methyl]ethanamine.

N-methylhydroxylamine and 3-(3,4-dimethoxyphenyl)prop-2-enoic acid react together in the presence of 2,2-dimethylpropanoyl chloride, n,n-diethylethanamine, ethyl acetate, ethoxyethane, n,n-dimethylformamide, chlorane to produce 3-(3,4-dimethoxyphenyl)-n-hydroxy-n-methylprop-2-enamide.

8-chloro-7-[(4-chlorophenyl)methyl]-3-ethyl-1-(3-hydroxypropyl)purine-2,6-dione reacts in the presence of propan-1-ol, sodium to produce 7-[(4-chlorophenyl)methyl]-3-ethyl-1-(3-hydroxypropyl)-8-propoxypurine-2,6-dione.

3-[4-(3-aminopropyl)phenyl]-1h-pyridazin-6-one and 2-chloroethanesulfonyl chloride react together in the presence of bromane, oxolane, n,n-diethylethanamine, 1,3-dimethylimidazolidin-2-one to produce n-[3-[4-(6-oxo-1h-pyridazin-3-yl)phenyl]propyl]ethenesulfonamide.
